A trusted source of legal news related to cryptocurrencies.

Also referred to by its acronym, CLAG, the organization releases memoranda on a regular basis assessing legal issues related to cryptocurrencies with most topics expected to be Bitcoin related.  The organization also holds a conference annually.

The organization was announced on April 10, 2012 (1.1).

##Memoranda

